    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_va8RPODG8FYPoxPO",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Durability Like Never Before: </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_WszPVAbP6EgZ1WkV",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>The Toughest SMARTWATCH YET.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_sr808u76TtoSOrNK",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Crafted with a premium zinc alloy body and a third-generation Gorilla Glass screen, the Carbinox Blaze stands as the toughest smartwatch we&apos;ve ever engineered.  The thicker, more resistant straps ensure that no matter how intense your day gets, your Blaze will be right there with you, taking the hits and pushing through.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_WCQSuOQu090er99Q",
      "label": "Rectangle 11"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_WCQSuOQu090er99Q_tablet",
      "label": "Rectangle 11 tablet"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_ij0Cld0GNtqNk1Xq",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>AI Voice Assistant at Your Command,</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_OWMPMfC768HiYjXZ",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Ready to reply and send messages.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_TrMe3LL4sJswonZe",
      "label": "The Carbinox Blaze takes convenience to the next level with its built-",
      "default": "<p>The Carbinox Blaze takes convenience to the next level with its built-in AI voice assistant. </p><p></p><p>Seamlessly paired with your smartphone, you can send and reply to SMS messages using simple voice commands—no need to stop what you’re doing. </p><p></p><p>Whether you&apos;re on the job or on the go, the AI assistant keeps you connected, hands-free.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_EXLwJ5MZK8ds2Xg0",
      "label": "Rectangle 11"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_EXLwJ5MZK8ds2Xg0_tablet",
      "label": "Rectangle 11 tablet"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_qi2WGkLHekc2mCfJ",
      "label": "Navigate Your World:",
      "default": "<p>Navigate Your World: </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_jJt5C7Qtv4wZura5",
      "label": "Introducing GPS with Unmatched Precision",
      "default": "<p>Introducing GPS with Unmatched Precision</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_lz0toSMQiDuWk6qV",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>The Carbinox Blaze is our first smartwatch equipped with state-of-the-art GPS technology. Whether you’re navigating a job site or exploring off the beaten path, it will keep you on track with reliable, accurate positioning.  This feature can be easily enjoyed by selecting any of the sports modes on your smartwatch..</p>"
    },
