        "text_WszPVAbP6EgZ1WkV": "<p>The Toughest SMARTWATCH YET.</p>",
        "text_sr808u76TtoSOrNK": "<p>Crafted with a premium zinc alloy body and a third-generation Gorilla Glass screen, the Carbinox Blaze stands as the toughest smartwatch we&apos;ve ever engineered.  The thicker, more resistant straps ensure that no matter how intense your day gets, your Blaze will be right there with you, taking the hits and pushing through.</p>",
